HONORABLE BOARD OF SUPERVISORS,
City and County of San Francisco,
City Hall.
Members:
I am forwarding herewith draft of resolution
instructing the Mayor and Clerk of your Board to sign
an agreement with the Market Street Railway Company
giving the City the right to construct and maintain
a water pipe line beneath the Company's tracks, near
Iomita Park, San Mateo County, California.
Said water
pipe line is to convey water to the Municipal Air Port.
I respectfully recommend the adoption of the
attached resolution.
Very traly yours,
M. M. O' SHAUGHNESSY,
City Engineer.
